title: Stossel.2014.WS.SDTV-MiXED
description:
John F. Stossel is an American consumer reporter, investigative journalist, author, libertarian columnist, and former co-anchor for the ABC News show 20/20. In this show he looks at consumer-focused topics, such as civil liberties, the business of health care, and free trade.

THESE ARE NOT SCENE RIPS. All rips without "XAiO" in the filename were ripped by skJGZV6z over at TPB. Thanks go out to him. I've got the rest of Stossel, including new episodes. As well as The Independents. I've also been ripping Kennedy. Not sure when I'll post what. Let's see what the interest in this torrent is like first.
